data.description: Step into this like-new, move-in ready, cozy one-story home, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms that bathe in natural light, thanks to the open floor plan and ample windows. The kitchen overlooks the dining and living room, equipped with a long breakfast bar, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Vinyl flooring graces the kitchen, living, and dining areas, adding a touch of elegance. All bedrooms offer plenty of space, with the primary bedroom boasting an ensuite. The backyard provides ample room for your creative ideas to flourish. Don't miss the opportunity to explore the possibilities and make this your home sweet home!
